<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title || 'About PRATHA Project' %></title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f9f0 0%, #e8f5e9 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2c7744, #4da167, #a3de83);
            border-bottom: 3px solid #d8e3c8;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding-top: 0.4rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            color: #ffffff !important;
            font-family: 'Gill Sans', 'Gill Sans MT', Calibri, 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            margin-right: 1rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: #f8fff8 !important;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .nav-content {
            margin-right: 50px;
        }
        
        /* About Section - Only Mission */
        .about-section {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .about-section h2 {
            color: #2c7744;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .about-section strong {
            color: #2c7744;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2c7744, #4da167, #a3de83);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-section {
                margin: 40px 20px;
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .about-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .about-section p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Navigation Bar -->
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg shadow-sm fixed-top">
    <div class="nav-content container-fluid px-4">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
            <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="logo" width="60" height="60" class="me-3 logo-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-semibold fs-5" href="/">
                Center for Indian Knowledge Systems, IIT Guwahati
            </a>
        </div>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/about">About</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/Herbal-Ai">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot"></i> HerbalAI Chat
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- ✅ ONLY MISSION SECTION -->
<div class="about-section">
    <h2><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Our Mission 🌿</h2>
    
    <p>
        The <strong>PRATHA Project</strong> aims to bridge traditional wisdom with modern scientific approaches by recording, studying, and analyzing Assam's indigenous health systems. We collaborate with local healers, researchers, and students to create a comprehensive digital repository of medicinal plants, therapies, and ethnomedicinal practices.
    </p>
    
    <p>
        This initiative is supported by <strong>AYUSH, Government of Assam</strong> in collaboration with <strong>Centre for Indian Knowledge Systems (CIKS), IIT Guwahati</strong>, aligning with the broader goal of promoting sustainable, community-based healthcare solutions.
    </p>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Center for Indian Knowledge Systems, IIT Guwahati. All rights reserved.</p>
        <small>Preserving traditional wisdom for future generations</small>
    </div>
</footer>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>